{"tid":84572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 有冇眼科醫生？","createTime":"2017-01-17T15:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T16:21:22.000Z","uid":2037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83f5fd439fb98639f598edc356479a2ef1d41638","tid":84572,"uid":2037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"我琴日(30個鐘前) 比個波好大力咁省中左眼位置<br />\n事發後大約1分鐘後開始慢慢睇得返嘢同流完眼水<br />\n但係問題就嚟 我睇嘢嘅時候 左眼明顯睇少左嘢<br />\n好似有啲嘢遮住左我隻左眼咁 <br />\n類似幅圖圈住嘅形狀同位置 <br />\n幅圖代表我整個左眼視角<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/233346_c806e1b5f6867c798bf3e6d017875645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F233346_c806e1b5f6867c798bf3e6d017875645.jpg&h=cc11ec91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係我仍然睇到嘢 隻眼亦都唔痛<br />\n咁我以為撞到啫 少事啦應該 第日就冇事<br />\n<br />\n第日起身 發現好似好返啲 個影冇咁明顯<br />\n咁我估就好返啦 直到夜晚<br />\n夜晚我處於一個比較上暗嘅地方<br />\n就發現遮住我左眼嗰個影特別明顯<br />\n個影係黑黑地嘅<br />\n而當我合埋眼嘅時候 個影就變到白白地色<br />\n類似你合埋眼嗰陣見到光嘅嗰種色<br />\n而且 我發現我左眼睇嘅嘢少左<br />\n例子：<br />\n我瞓係到 約45&deg;望住橫樑 <br />\n我右眼（冇撞親）望到我著緊嘅衫<br />\n但係左眼望唔到 個視角完全比嘢遮住左<br />\n<br />\n我好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打可以幫我<br />\n或者介紹醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a884eb864075d4f487ba696ccfd6c7a38dbbd2f","tid":84572,"uid":2037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2bec300d9d8efa0d8f601c230b6bc3043e4f24","tid":84572,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"又黑又白， 仲唔係火車頭甩皮痴係你隻眼到，洗個面無事<br />\n<br />\n利申 7up"},{"pid":"cd70b895c844c1b398b