 發現好似好返啲 個影冇咁明顯<br />\n咁我估就好返啦 直到夜晚<br />\n夜晚我處於一個比較上暗嘅地方<br />\n就發現遮住我左眼嗰個影特別明顯<br />\n個影係黑黑地嘅<br />\n而當我合埋眼嘅時候 個影就變到白白地色<br />\n類似你合埋眼嗰陣見到光嘅嗰種色<br />\n而且 我發現我左眼睇嘅嘢少左<br />\n例子：<br />\n我瞓係到 約45&deg;望住橫樑 <br />\n我右眼（冇撞親）望到我著緊嘅衫<br />\n但係左眼望唔到 個視角完全比嘢遮住左<br />\n<br />\n我好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打可以幫我<br />\n或者介紹醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n林順潮眼科中心，朋友話唔錯，係就快d約，呢d嘢廢事拖過年啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fa361b4648da49124c375c97be1d40f0860430","tid":84572,"uid":62596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3e2fbe4c1316572afb8eaa5e9527db92a7f996","tid":84572,"uid":13831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"認真就去睇醫生啦好唔好，幾百蚊買個安心<br />\n<br />\n唔好攞隻眼冒險，太重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c8c739ed3b8b266fcf48d14bed14a0fde288d7","tid":84572,"uid":35040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<br />\n祝早日康復"},{"pid":"6dd4a6b4a483af81244f27d40983cb878257f6a0","tid":84572,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"搭單問 隻眼比手指整到<br />\n睇野有近視好濛<br />\n睇完專科都係咁<br />\n佢話有曈孔係傷口<br />\n睇野濛唔關傷口事<br />\n傷咩好返左<br />\n可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇野仲係濛 半個月都黎"},{"pid":"64423550b60e026703ff181b2261b0d173d7a07e","tid":84572,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":